OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FCorrupt police officer     
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fhotline goes nationwide    
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, An anti-corruption hotline to report   
OL,6, corruption in the Metropolitan Police  
OL,7, is being launched nationwide.          
OL,9,FThe service, run by Crimestoppers, was 
OL,10,Flaunched for the force in November 2022
OL,11,Fand has seen almost 3,000 online       
OL,12,Freports and calls regarding the force. 
OL,14,FIt is used to report officers and staff
OL,15,Ffor corruption, abuse and other        
OL,16,Fbreaches of trust or power.            
OL,18,FThe chairman of the National Police    
OL,19,FChiefs' Council said it would enable   
OL,20,Fthem to "take action".                 
